    + "F11 (&-)"    Function FuncSendFKey 11
    + "F12"(&=)"    Function FuncSendFKey 12

DestroyFunc FuncSendFKey
AddToFunc FuncSendFKey
+ I Key F$0  A N  -
+ I FakeKeypress depth 2 press F$0 wait 10 release F$0 wait 10
+ I Key F$0  A N  GotoDesk 0 $0

